commit message: Fix default value of watch background enabled
Always have a PinWatcher on a Pin
Underline name when post has email
Keep the red bar around for at least 2 seconds

Better notifications:
Fix the intent
Launch the thread the notification is about, or when it shows multiple threads, show the pinned drawer.
Change Volley to be less verbose when not compiled in debug

Make Volley use normal String concatenation in ImageLoader.java
The java compiler will make this a StringBuilder if it needs to be.
Volley doesn't call finalize functions inside some classes
Useless synchronized with local only variable
Enable proguard for optimizations and removing dead code
Use an adapter for the board spinner.
Fix for bug when slidable wasn't updated and improved tablet layouts
Add link to the board editor at the bottom of the board spinner.
Cleanup res/ folder. Add license headers.
Add option to force the phone layout.
Only update last seen when watching is enabled.
Added lastseenpost to loadables, fixed PinWatcher
Set timer to 1s when starting the app/toggling watching a pin
Saving scroll position when opening replies.
Made the board editor filler an option.
